---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="page-heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">about</p>
    <h1>Hands-on technical generalist</h1>
  </section>
  <section class="about-body">
    <p>
      The point of notsoosleepy is proof of work. Homelab experiments,
      infrastructure notes, debugging records, and project writeups all end up here with
      enough context that future me, teammates, or recruiters can see how I
      think through problems.
    </p>
    <p>
      The writing is intentionally practical: what I tried, what broke, what I
      changed, and what I would do differently next time.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
